      <title>印尼学生要求总统在民意调查前保持中立</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesian-students-demand-president-remain-neutral-ahead-poll-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名组织者称，数百名印度尼西亚学生将于周三举行抗议活动，抗议即将卸任的总统佐科·维多多(Joko Widodo)涉嫌干预2月14日取代世界第三大民主国家领导人的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesian-students-demand-president-remain-neutral-ahead-poll-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:33:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国和卡塔尔国防部长同意加强军事关系 - 首尔</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-qatar-defence-ministers-agree-boost-military-ties-seoul-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔国防部周三表示，在首尔推动全球武器销售的背景下，韩国和卡塔尔国防部长已同意扩大联合军事训练并加强双边合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-qatar-defence-ministers-agree-boost-military-ties-seoul-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:29:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国恒大：负债开发商整顿背后的人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-people-behind-indebted-developers-overhaul-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[来自 Alvarez &amp; 的重组专家马萨尔将依靠与中国的联系和复杂的企业改革的记录，试图为房地产巨头恒大设计一个涉及债权人、当局和购房者的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-people-behind-indebted-developers-overhaul-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:18:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国与蒙古建立战略伙伴关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-mongolia-enter-into-strategic-partnership-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社看到的一份文件草案显示，德国和蒙古正在建立战略伙伴关系，因为两国都希望在包括采矿业在内的许多政策领域进行更密切的合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/germany-mongolia-enter-into-strategic-partnership-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾南部山体滑坡掩埋两辆巴士 造成11人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landslide-southern-philippines-buries-two-buses-injures-11-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[灾难官员周三表示，菲律宾南部省份暴雨引发的山体滑坡掩埋了两辆巴士，造成至少 11 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landslide-southern-philippines-buries-two-buses-injures-11-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 03:21:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本航空坠机事件：空中交通管制员呼吁“大幅”增加员工</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-airlines-crash-air-traffic-controllers-call-significant-staff-increase-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月东京羽田机场发生致命空难后，代表日本空中交通管制员的工会呼吁“大幅增加”员工，以改善机场运营的安全性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-airlines-crash-air-traffic-controllers-call-significant-staff-increase-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 03:12:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市上涨，很大程度上得益于中国的稳定努力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周三走强，投资者在观望北京为支撑低迷股市而采取的日益疯狂的举措是否真正有效，而债券则因近期抛售而有所缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 02:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国驻荷兰大使馆表示绝不允许网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-embassy-netherlands-says-china-would-never-allow-cyberattacks-2024-02-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国驻荷兰大使馆周三发表声明称，中方绝不允许任何中国实体和个人进行网络攻击等非法活动，也绝不允许利用中国设施进行此类攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-embassy-netherlands-says-china-would-never-allow-cyberattacks-2024-02-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 01:17:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
